	<Title>
		Migraine treatment: Can antidepressants help?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Certain antidepressants are used in migraine treatment. Learn more about these medications.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		My doctor prescribed an antidepressant for my migraines. Is this an appropriate migraine treatment? I don&apos;t have depression.
	</Question>
